entries.femaleVariant: My… my favorite arm.  It's... gone!
Scavs... they klepped it. While I… I was sleepin'. An' if they got it… it's… gone forever.
Oh God, th-they'll kill me next! And I wasted my whole life!
Choom, you sold it for a spot of skag. That was two months ago.
This's the new one your mom got you.
